OL,3,CFolye MLA Gary Middleton resigning to
OL,4,Cdeal with mental health challenges
OL,6,FDUP MLA Gary Middleton is to step back
OL,7,Ffrom public life to deal with mental
OL,8,Fhealth challenges.
OL,10,FThe Foyle representative has said he
OL,11,Fwill resign as an MLA on Friday.
OL,13,FParty leader Gavin Robinson has paid
OL,14,Ftribute to Mr Middleton, stating he
OL,15,Fhad been a "dedicated and steadfast
OL,16,Fservant to people across the city of
OL,17,FLondonderry and surrounding areas".
OL,26,@wD@LOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
