PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775772667
OL,3,CFolye MLA Gary Middleton resigning to
OL,4,Cdeal with mental health challenges
OL,6,FMr Middleton has been an MLA in the
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland Assembly since 2015,
OL,8,Fhaving previously been elected as a
OL,9,Fcouncillor.
OL,11,FIn a statement Mr Middleton said:
OL,12,F"Over the last few months, I have been
OL,13,Fsuffering from a bout of ill-health
OL,14,Fwhich has significantly limited my
OL,15,Fability to represent my constituents
OL,16,Fin the way I always have.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775772667
OL,3,CFolye MLA Gary Middleton resigning to
OL,4,Cdeal with mental health challenges
OL,6,F"I had hoped to be able to return to
OL,7,Fwork and to recover, but I have come
OL,8,Fto the point of accepting that if I am
OL,9,Fto focus on getting back to full
OL,10,Fhealth, I cannot do this whilst
OL,11,Fremaining in public office.
OL,13,F"It would have been easier for me to
OL,14,Fwithdraw from the political arena
OL,15,Fquietly and without explanation but I
OL,16,Fwanted my constituents and the wider
OL,17,Fcommunity to understand that I am
OL,18,Fleaving public life because I am
OL,19,Fsuffering significant mental health
OL,20,Fchallenges."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775772667
OL,3,CFolye MLA Gary Middleton resigning to
OL,4,Cdeal with mental health challenges
OL,6,FHe added: "I am journeying through a
OL,7,Fdifficult experience and have been for
OL,8,Fsome time.
OL,10,F"I am receiving treatment thanks to
OL,11,Fthe wonderful services afforded to me
OL,12,Fby our National Health Service.
OL,14,F"The support and encouragement from my
OL,15,Ffamily and friends, combined with the
OL,16,Fexpert treatment I am receiving has
OL,17,Fgiven me hope and I can see a glimmer
OL,18,Fof light in what has been a very dark
OL,19,Ftunnel.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775772667
OL,3,CFolye MLA Gary Middleton resigning to
OL,4,Cdeal with mental health challenges
OL,6,F"In making this statement I want to
OL,7,Fgive encouragement to those who may be
OL,8,Fon a similar journey by highlighting
OL,9,Fthat help is available.
OL,11,F"I have learned in recent times that
OL,12,Fit's okay not to be okay."
OL,14,FThe statement concluded: "I want to
OL,15,Fthank all those who have supported me
OL,16,Fin Foyle over the years and who
OL,17,Fbestowed the privilege of electing me,
OL,18,Ffirst into local government and then
OL,19,Fto the Northern Ireland Assembly.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUtD@ZO]vD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775772667
OL,3,CFolye MLA Gary Middleton resigning to
OL,4,Cdeal with mental health challenges
OL,6,F"Finally, I want to thank all my
OL,7,Fcolleagues in the DUP for their
OL,8,Fsupport and friendship, to my staff
OL,9,Ffor their loyalty and to my wife and
OL,10,Ffamily who have been my rock during
OL,11,Fthis period.
OL,13,F"I will always be grateful for all the
OL,14,Fsupport shown to me.
OL,16,F"I will resign as a Member of the
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland Assembly tomorrow
OL,18,F(Friday).
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775772667
OL,3,CFolye MLA Gary Middleton resigning to
OL,4,Cdeal with mental health challenges
OL,6,F"As I depart the public stage, I want
OL,7,Fto wish all those who serve the public
OL,8,Fand with whom I have had the privilege
OL,9,Fto serve alongside, regardless of
OL,10,Fparty affiliations, every best wish
OL,11,Ffor the future."
OL,13,FDUP leader Mr Robinson said his party
OL,14,Fcolleague had been a "consistent voice
OL,15,Ffor unionism in Foyle".
OL,17,FHe said: "As the sole unionist MLA in
OL,18,FFoyle, Gary Middleton has been a
OL,19,Fdedicated and steadfast servant to
OL,20,Fpeople across the city of Londonderry
OL,21,Fand surrounding areas.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@PO]vD@VOUwD@VO]yD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775772667
OL,3,CFolye MLA Gary Middleton resigning to
OL,4,Cdeal with mental health challenges
OL,6,F"Since 2015, he has been a strong and
OL,7,Fconsistent voice in the Northern
OL,8,FIreland Assembly and was never afraid
OL,9,Fto stand up for what he believed was
OL,10,Fright.
OL,12,F"Elected in May 2011 as a Councillor
OL,13,Fat just 20 years of age, Gary was
OL,14,Foften the youngest in the room but
OL,15,Fearned the respect of colleagues
OL,16,Fthrough his incredible ability to
OL,17,Farticulate the concerns of the people
OL,18,Fof Foyle.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775772667
OL,3,CFolye MLA Gary Middleton resigning to
OL,4,Cdeal with mental health challenges
OL,6,F"In being such a clear and consistent
OL,7,Fvoice for unionism in Foyle, Gary has
OL,8,Fat times faced threats from
OL,9,Frepublicans.
OL,11,F"That pressure never silenced him nor
OL,12,Fdeterred him, he continued to stand
OL,13,Ffirm for his constituents and his
OL,14,Fprinciples."
OL,16,FMr Robinson added: "While we deeply
OL,17,Fregret that Gary is leaving public
OL,18,Fservice, we will do all we can to
OL,19,Fsupport him.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@LO]xD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775772667
OL,3,CFolye MLA Gary Middleton resigning to
OL,4,Cdeal with mental health challenges
OL,6,F"Gary's focus must now be on his
OL,7,Frecovery, and he will have the support
OL,8,Fof colleagues, both inside and outside
OL,9,Four ranks, on his journey.
OL,11,F"On behalf of the Democratic Unionist
OL,12,FParty, I want to sincerely thank Gary
OL,13,Ffor his years of service and
OL,14,Fdedication.
OL,16,F"Many people in the Foyle constituency
OL,17,Fhave been positively impacted as a
OL,18,Fresult of Gary's devotion to his
OL,19,Fcommunity.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/11
